## Project Purpose

Python orchestrator that runs on a Vast.ai GPU instance. Manages:
- Model download from HuggingFace Hub
- vLLM server lifecycle
- GPU metrics streaming agent (FastAPI on :9100)
- Warmup phase orchestration
- Health checks aggregating both services
- CLI commands: `start`, `stop`, `status`, `logs`, `doctor`, `scenarios`

This runs IN the GPU container. Talks to the Node.js app server externally over HTTP.

