## Lifecycle Step Pattern

Each file in `src/lifecycle/` exports one main function. The orchestrator chains them.

```python
# src/lifecycle/start_vllm.py
def start_in_tmux(scenario, log_file: str):
    """Start vLLM in tmux session 'vllm'. Returns when process is launched (not when ready)."""
    command = " ".join(scenario.build_vllm_command())
    tmux.create_session("vllm", command, log_file)
    log.info(f"vLLM launched in tmux. Log: {log_file}")
    log.info(f"  Attach: tmux attach -t vllm")
